  }, "Learn how others"), " have implemented them, what their key needs were, and the various patterns, before designing your own."), mdx("p", null, "Nonetheless, remember that we\u2019re not building in a vacuum. Unless we\u2019re working in a brand new startup, we\u2019ll have existing systems to integrate or work around\u2014it\u2019s almost never an option to sweep it all away and start from scratch with the latest and greatest. Respect the existing systems that have been chugging along and invest the effort to learn why and how they solve existing problems. "), mdx("h2", {
